long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Have you ever wanted to completely ignore the fact Ch*lsea exists to ease your internal suffering? Then the Ch*lsea to Fulham-ifier is for you! Enjoy browsing the Web snacking on a Fulham Bun, tying Fulham knots, and reading Hello! magazine articles about Fulham Davy.

As giants of the football world, Fulham have won it all. As 2010 Europa League finalists, 1975 FA Cup finalists, and champions of the 2001 Football League Division One, no other club can touch Fulham in terms of glory. Particularly not Ch*lsea, with their 6 league titles, 2 Champions League wins, and 8 FA Cups.
